Al BARLOW, Administrator of the Estate of Ned Peterson, Deceased, v. UNITED STATES of America. No. 1737. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. Jan. 9, 1939. Lawrence E. Goldman, of Kansas City, Mo., for appellant. Summerfield S. Alexander, U. S. Atty., of Topeka, Kan.

Before PHILLIPS, BRATTON, and WILLIAMS, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed on motion of appellant at appellant’s costs.
